      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "五路天官"
      ],
      "text": "将一应财源，献与福主。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00038",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "催旺",
        "时运"
      ],
      "text": "领法旨。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00039",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "催旺、时运同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00040",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "五路天官"
      ],
      "text": "我等先赠其财，后赐其福，真乃财源辐辏也。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00041",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同斗鹌鹑",
      "speakers": [
        "五路天官"
      ],
      "text": "这的是广众福田临，今日个添来福份尽。堂前五路将军，齐献那财源茂盛。高照着赐福天官祥瑞呈，玳筵前满泛着——",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00042",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "五路天官"
      ],
      "text": "哎——",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00043",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同斗鹌鹑",
      "speakers": [
        "五路天官"
      ],
      "text": "金樽，听笙歌一派贺升平，要与那福主称庆。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00044",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "催旺、时运引四回回招聚宝盒同上。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00045",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "催旺",
        "时运"
      ],
      "text": "一群财源献上。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00046",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "五路天官"
      ],
      "text": "妙啊！缕缕银光透，层层金气浮。好一座金穴银山也！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00047",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同上小楼",
      "speakers": [
        "五路天官"
      ],
      "text": "只见那金银，灿灿灿光明，喜的是金穴银山，库满箱盈。齐祝银屏，事业丰隆，龟鹤宏源，陶朱堪趁，一任价东西行运。",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00048",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖吹打〗。五路天官同下高台。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00049",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "五路天官"
      ],
      "text": "幅辏已全，一同回奏上帝者。请。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00050",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同煞尾",
      "speakers": [
        "五路天官"
      ],
      "text": "听悠扬一派洞仙音，齐齐的跨鹤乘鸾上码云。看话日光天，风调雨顺，指日里称庆丰年定太平。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001008_e00051",
      "play_id": "02001008",
      "scene_id": "02001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众车同斜门拥众人同下。",
      "text_length": 11
    }
  ],
